      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera represents a pinnacle of mechanical preservation. Powered by a 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, the internal combustion cycle remains flawless with a perfectly linear torque curve. The critical IMS bearing has been proactively replaced with a dual-row ceramic retrofit, ensuring the structural integrity of the rotating assembly. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers crisp gate engagement, paired with a chassis that retains factory-spec kinematics and damping rates. Equipped with four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors, the braking system provides immediate bite and zero fade. This is an investment-grade example with no deferred maintenance and a pristine undercarriage.",
